HEADWORD: Fond
<hw>Fond</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <mark>obs.</mark> <def><pos>imp.</pos> of
<er>Find</er>. Found.</def> <rj><au>Chaucer.</au></rj>⟦br⟧
